4
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:07,370
If someone took everything away from me,

5
00:00:07,370 --> 00:00:11,010
my business, my investments,
all my money in the bank

6
00:00:11,010 --> 00:00:13,340
would I be able to start from scratch

7
00:00:13,340 --> 00:00:15,370
and become a multimillionaire again?

8
00:00:15,370 --> 00:00:16,280
Well, funnily enough,

9
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:18,160
that's the exact same question.

10
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:19,510
I asked Richard Branson

11
00:00:19,510 --> 00:00:21,360
when I was around his house having lunch.

12
00:00:21,360 --> 00:00:23,430
Well, the short answer is the same as his.

13
00:00:23,430 --> 00:00:25,580
Yes, I would be able to achieve it again.

14
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:26,860
But what I really think is

15
00:00:26,860 --> 00:00:27,870
I'll be able to achieve it

16
00:00:27,870 --> 00:00:29,970
in around about half the time or less.

17
00:00:29,970 --> 00:00:30,843
But, of course, the interest, in part,

18
00:00:30,843 --> 00:00:34,260
