22
00:00:39,850 --> 00:00:43,543
One, I have to do it from
a starting date of 2020.

23
00:00:43,543 --> 00:00:46,240
Two, I go back to being 16 year old.

24
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:50,270
And three, I keep all my
business and investing knowledge.

25
00:00:50,270 --> 00:00:51,300
Now, the challenge will be

26
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:53,230
to find the fastest way to move

27
00:00:53,230 --> 00:00:56,740
from employee, to
self-employed, to business owner

28
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:58,690
