33
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:09,610
If you listen and use the information

34
00:01:09,610 --> 00:01:11,120
I'm about to share with you,

35
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:13,200
you could be the next millionaire.

36
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,140
But the first step

37
00:01:14,140 --> 00:01:17,120
along the path is to
smash that like button.

38
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:17,953
Okay, then.

39
00:01:17,953 --> 00:01:20,120
So, we've got to get
ourselves into that age pod

40
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:23,613
which is going to make
me 36 years younger.

41
00:01:23,613 --> 00:01:24,590
I like the sound of that.

42
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:26,730
Just imagine a 16 year old me.

43
00:01:26,730 --> 00:01:27,740
I've just left school

44
00:01:27,740 --> 00:01:29,310
