47
00:01:32,410 --> 00:01:33,250
To top it all off

48
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:35,950
the world has experienced
a global pandemic

49
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:38,100
causing unemployment to rise

50
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:39,300
