55
00:01:45,790 --> 00:01:47,370
but in my opinion

56
00:01:47,370 --> 00:01:49,990
this new world offers opportunities

57
00:01:49,990 --> 00:01:51,410
more than you might first think,

58
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:53,240
especially, if you know where to look.

59
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,910
So, you can keep track of the challenge.

60
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:56,600
I'm going to put a counter down here.

61
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,260
It's going to track the time

62
00:01:58,260 --> 00:01:59,350
