64
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:03,020
So, let's set it to zero

65
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:04,300
and get started.

66
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:05,773
Where's all my money gone?

67
00:02:05,773 --> 00:02:06,606
(television beeping)

68
00:02:06,606 --> 00:02:07,610
- My first move will be getting

69
00:02:07,610 --> 00:02:09,480
the highest paid job possible.

70
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:12,410
Now, if this is at minimum
wage working for McDonald's

71
00:02:12,410 --> 00:02:14,420
or Walmart or anything like that,

72
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:15,490
