73
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:17,560
The aim isn't to be comfortable.

74
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:20,030
That's actually the worst thing it can be.

75
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,740
When you get paid just enough

76
00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:23,100
to make you comfortable

77
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:25,080
