78
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,460
and that makes you forget all your dreams.

79
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:29,140
The only purpose of this job is

80
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:31,100
to establish an income stream.

81
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:33,070
Without money, it's very, very hard

82
00:02:33,070 --> 00:02:34,400
to accomplish anything.

83
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,350
Instead of thinking of it as a drug,

84
00:02:36,350 --> 00:02:38,090
I will be using it as fuel

85
00:02:38,090 --> 00:02:40,000
to propel me towards my goals.

86
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,830
My second move will be to
establish a side hustle

87
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:44,690
or side job of some sort.

88
00:02:44,690 --> 00:02:48,550
The pandemic has fast tracked
the digital revolution.

89
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:51,250
Online shopping is more popular than ever.

90
00:02:51,250 --> 00:02:53,780
And the internet is an unbelievable tool

91
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:55,080
for our new entrepreneurs.

92
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:58,450
Online marketing would be the
number one high-income skill

93
00:02:58,450 --> 00:02:59,800
that I would want to learn.

94
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,930
The best way for me to do that

95
00:03:01,930 --> 00:03:03,630
and make some money on the side

96
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:06,130
would be to set up a drop shipping store.

97
00:03:06,130 --> 00:03:09,370
Drop shipping is when you take
a product from a supplier,

98
00:03:09,370 --> 00:03:11,600
market and advertise it online

99
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,680
and then get the supplier
to ship it directly

100
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,070
to the customer for you,

101
00:03:15,070 --> 00:03:17,370
allowing you to make a small profit

102
00:03:17,370 --> 00:03:19,980
without even physically touching the item.

103
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:22,220
On YouTube, drop shipping is advertised

104
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:24,350
as this awesome way to make lots of money

105
00:03:24,350 --> 00:03:25,820
without doing any work.

106
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:26,653
Do you know what?

107
00:03:26,653 --> 00:03:27,950
That's not really the reality.

108
00:03:27,950 --> 00:03:29,970
Running a profitable drop shipping store

109
00:03:29,970 --> 00:03:32,770
requires you to learn
the basics of business,

110
00:03:32,770 --> 00:03:35,070
how to run ads on social media,

111
00:03:35,070 --> 00:03:36,420
how to build a website,

112
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,560
how to write in a way

113
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:40,270
that makes people want
to buy, graphic design,

114
00:03:40,270 --> 00:03:42,490
and, in some cases, video editing.

115
00:03:42,490 --> 00:03:45,260
I've approached lots of
local businesses and shops

116
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:46,850
and talked to them about the stock

117
00:03:46,850 --> 00:03:47,960
they've got sitting around

118
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,170
that they can't sell.

119
00:03:49,170 --> 00:03:51,470
Almost every business has stock

120
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:52,800
it wants to get rid of.

121
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,310
And, normally, this will be, you know,

122
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:56,300
the end of the line product, for example.

123
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:57,860
Some of it has gone a bit out of date

124
00:03:57,860 --> 00:04:00,080
and with all my online
marketing knowledge.

125
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,630
I've been the perfect
position to help them.

126
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:04,140
So, you can say, look, I'll tell you what,

127
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:06,690
I'll give you 50% of what I sell it for.

128
00:04:06,690 --> 00:04:08,070
Now, if that's in cash

129
00:04:08,070 --> 00:04:10,490
any business owner's
going to be very happy.

130
00:04:10,490 --> 00:04:12,160
It's a win-win situation.

131
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:15,750
I'm a big fan of learning
while you're earning.

132
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:18,910
And this is where I would
take a real step back here

133
00:04:18,910 --> 00:04:20,490
and take a deep breath

134
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:22,180
before taking on the hurdle

135
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:23,478
