145
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:41,610
To avoid this

146
00:04:41,610 --> 00:04:44,940
I would create a budget and
stick to it religiously.

147
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:46,350
I need to have enough money

148
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:49,180
