unexpected comes up.

153
00:04:58,770 --> 00:05:00,850
And that will help me stay out of debt.

154
00:05:00,850 --> 00:05:05,400
Two, invest in a pension account
every year, without fail.

155
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:07,440
Three, open a Vanguard account

156
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:09,390
