191
00:06:17,170 --> 00:06:19,930
When people feel a personal
connection towards you

192
00:06:19,930 --> 00:06:22,400
then it opens up many, many doors.

193
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:24,200
Even more than you could imagine.

194
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:27,130
My fourth move would
happen the day I turned 18.

195
00:06:27,130 --> 00:06:29,190
It will be getting a credit card.

196
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:30,430
In my opinion, this is one

197
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:32,430
